      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in an irreproachable state, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, its mechanical performance is indistinguishable from new. This offering represents a definitive acquisition for the connoisseur seeking a specimen of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
