    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this absolute gem in person. It\u2019s been my total pride and joy, kept in such pristine shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s as smooth as it is beautiful, this is definitely the one for you! I'm a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy.",
      "price": 46500.0,
