    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a pristine E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six powerplant, boasting an 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example is mechanically superlative; the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has undergone preventative reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with no bushing deflection, riding on unblemished Style 67 forged alloys. The exterior finish remains in showroom state with deep luster and no clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather shows zero bolster wear. A definitive, investment-grade specimen for the BMW purist.",
